name: DubuqueChoraleCalendar
0:
”Alexa open Chorale Calendar”
”what concerts are happening on August 24th?”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chorale calendar
des: This skill provides updated information from the web for the Dubuque Chorale's schedule of concerts and rehearsals. Information is gathered through their online live calendar and will be sent to your Alexa app upon request.
